      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive models were adopted for Ti-6Al-4V implant components and UHMWPE block, consistent with the elastic-dominated regime of the F1717 test. Contact between screw and rod was modeled with frictional contact (mu=0.23). Model form assumptions are documented and justified relative to the QoIs of interest."
