      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions were mapped directly from the F1717 fixture geometry and load application points. Material property inputs to the model were drawn from the same measurement campaign as the experimental constructs. A formal input equivalency table was prepared and reviewed by the V&V team confirming alignment between simulation and test."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
