      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed for three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement). The validation metric E/uval was computed for each QoI incorporating experimental variability and model uncertainty. All E/uval values were below 1.96. Percentage differences ranged from 1.3% to 7.8%, all within the pre-specified 10% acceptance bound. Gradation 3 achieved."
