      "rationale": "The three selected QoIs (construct stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) directly correspond to the performance characteristics evaluated in the F1717 regulatory standard and are the quantities used in the submission's design verification claim. Their relevance to the COU is explicitly documented in the simulation plan."
